{"data":[{"name":"101:1","price":"ഭയങ്കരമായ ആ സംഭവം.","arabic":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6158,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"al-qāriʿatu ","translations":["The Striking Calamity","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["al-qāriʿatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2245]]}},{"name":"101:2","price":"ഭയങ്കരമായ സംഭവം എന്നാല്‍ എന്താകുന്നു?","arabic":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6159,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"mā al-qāriʿatu ","translations":["What","(is) the Striking Calamity","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","al-qāriʿatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,240],[2,240,2215]]}},{"name":"101:3","price":"ഭയങ്കരമായ സംഭവമെന്നാല്‍ എന്താണെന്ന് നിനക്കറിയുമോ?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6160,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā adrāka mā al-qāriʿatu ","translations":["And what","will make you know","what","(is) the Striking Calamity","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","adrāka","mā","al-qāriʿatu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2189],[2,2189,3639],[3,3639,3759],[4,3759,5464]]}},{"name":"101:4","price":"മനുഷ്യര്‍ ചിന്നിച്ചിതറിയ പാറ്റയെപ്പോലെ ആകുന്ന ദിവസം!","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6161,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yakūnu al-nāsu kal-farāshi al-mabthūthi ","translations":["(The) Day","will be","the mankind","like moths","scattered","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yakūnu","al-nāsu","kal-farāshi","al-mabthūthi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,1580],[3,1580,3150],[4,3150,4470],[5,4470,7355]]}},{"name":"101:5","price":"പര്‍വ്വതങ്ങള്‍ കടഞ്ഞു വിതറപ്പെട്ട പഞ്ഞു പോലെയും ആയിത്തീരും.","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6162,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"watakūnu al-jibālu kal-ʿih'ni al-manfūshi ","translations":["And will be","the mountains","like wool","fluffed up","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["watakūnu","al-jibālu","kal-ʿih'ni","al-manfūshi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2270],[3,2270,3360],[4,3360,7535]]}},{"name":"101:6","price":"അപ്പോള്‍ ഏതൊരാളുടെ തുലാസുകള്‍ ഘനം തൂങ്ങിയോ","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6163,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā man thaqulat mawāzīnuhu ","translations":["Then as for","(him) whose","(are) heavy","his scales","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","man","thaqulat","mawāzīnuhu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2000],[2,2000,2970],[3,2970,3900],[4,3900,5655]]}},{"name":"101:7","price":"അവന്‍ സംതൃപ്തമായ ജീവിതത്തിലായിരിക്കും.(1)","arabic":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6164,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1) സല്‍കര്‍മങ്ങളുടെ തുലാസ്സു തട്ടുകള്‍ക്ക് ഘനമുണ്ടെങ്കില്‍ പരലോകത്ത് സംതൃപ്തമായ ജീവിതം ഉറപ്പാണെന്നര്‍ത്ഥം. കര്‍മങ്ങളുടെ തൂക്കവും, അത് കണക്കാക്കാനുള്ള തുലാസ്സും അദൃശ്യലോകത്തെ യാഥാര്‍ഥ്യങ്ങളെന്ന നിലയില്‍ വിശുദ്ധഖുര്‍ആന്‍ നമുക്ക് വെളിപ്പെടുത്തിത്തന്ന കാര്യങ്ങളാണ്. അതിന്റെ വിശദാംശങ്ങള്‍ ഈ ഭൗതിക ലോകത്തുവെച്ച് നമുക്ക് ഗ്രഹിക്കാനാവില്ല.","lang":"ml","meta":{"transliteration":"fahuwa fī ʿīshatin rāḍiyatin ","translations":["Then he","(will be) in","a life","pleasant","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["fahuwa","fī","ʿīshatin","rāḍiyatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1160],[3,1160,2240],[4,2240,3785]]}},{"name":"101:8","price":"എന്നാല്‍ ഏതൊരാളുടെ തുലാസുകള്‍ തൂക്കം കുറഞ്ഞതായോ","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6165,"juzNu